      • addViewer

        void addViewer(TViewer viewer)
        Allows the addition of TViewer objects. This method is internally called by the addSimElement methods. For most SimElements, the add operation is basically an addition to the proper list. Adding a viewer might entail additional configuration, which justifies having the associated procedure in a standalone method.

      • setTime

        void setTime(double time)
        Sets the current time of the simulation (in milliseconds). Note that this method does not advance (or rewind) the simulation to the desired time, but rather just resets the clock.
        Parameters:
        time - new time.
